{{Top|leg}}
'''Clive''' was the older of two [[Chef/Legends|cooks]] serving on the [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] ''[[Reliable]]'', part of an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Navy/Legends|fleet]] blockading the [[ThonBoka]] nebula in [[3 BBY/Legends|3 BBY]]. He attempted to cheat [[Gambler/Legends|gambler]] [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], who had gained entrance to the ''Reliable'' posing as a trader, in a game of [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]]. His dealing from the bottom of the deck was clumsy, and Calrissian spotted it right away; it was also ineffective, as the cards he dealt gave the visitor a natural two-card twenty-three. When younger cook [[Merle]] let slip that the cruiser ''[[Courteous]]'' was in need of supplies, Clive kicked him under the table.<ref name="lando">''[[Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka]]''</ref>

